**8-HOUR RULE: You can build exactly 3 features well. Not 4. Not 5. Three.**

| # | Feature | Build Time | Demo Impact | Owner |
|---|---------|-----------|-------------|-------|
| 1 | [Core feature] | ~__hr | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ | [role] |
| 2 | [AI feature] | ~__hr | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | [role] |
| 3 | [Visual feature] | ~__hr | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | [role] |

**KILL LIST (do NOT build):**
- ❌ [Tempting but time-wasting feature 1]
- ❌ [Tempting but time-wasting feature 2]
- ❌ [Tempting but time-wasting feature 3]
- ❌ Authentication / Login flows
- ❌ Settings / Profile pages
- ❌ Any admin functionality

